- "waves of glory" metaphorically refers to the achievements and performances in the game; 
- "caught the waves" suggests the players have performed well; 
- "riding the crest of their goals" implies leading in the goals scored; 
- "storm of opposing goals" symbolizes the challenges posed by the opposing team's scoring.

